                <head>145. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>The Operations Coordinating Board Operations Plan for Yugoslavia was reviewed and
                    minor changes were made in its text by the <gloss target="#t_OCB1">OCB</gloss>
                    Board Assistants at a May 29 meeting. The text of the 1958 version of the report
                    is printed as <ref target="#d133">Document 133</ref>. A copy of the 1959 revised
                    version is in Department of State, <gloss target="#t_OCB1">OCB</gloss> Files:
                    Lot 62 <gloss target="#t_D1">D</gloss> 430, Yugoslavia.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
